RE Phil Let me know if this is okPST sounds good Original Message From Giron Darron C Sent Friday January PM To Love Phillip M McLaughlin Jr Errol Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Ryder Patrick Taylor Joey Winfree ONeal D Subject RE Phil Let me know if this is ok Ill be there DG Original Message From Love Phillip M Sent Friday January PM To Giron Darron C McLaughlin Jr Errol Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Ryder Patrick Taylor Joey Winfree ONeal D Subject FW Phil Let me know if this is ok Let ONeal know if you will be in or out so that we can get some fillers PL Original Message From Winfree ONeal D Sent Friday January PM To Love Phillip M Subject Phil Let me know if this is ok Gentlemen What Lets play poker Where The land of Pears When Thursday January th between pm Directions No key map so here goes South please find from Downtown Exit McHardShadow Creek hint its the first exit after the Beltway Take a left onto McHard and proceed to the end of McHard There will be a Conoco at the first Stop sign the next stop sign will say Country Place Proceed to the third stop Sign and take a left to The Lakes of Country Place Go to the Gurards gate You will visit Starleaf Go thru the gate and Take a left on River Birch drive Starleaf will be the rd street on the right My house is the th house on the left in the cul de sac address Starleaf Pearland Tx phone cell O

RE Phil Let me know if this is okPST sounds good Original Message From Giron Darron C Sent Friday January PM To Love Phillip M McLaughlin Jr Errol Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Ryder Patrick Taylor Joey Winfree ONeal D Subject RE Phil Let me know if this is ok Ill be there DG Original Message From Love Phillip M Sent Friday January PM To Giron Darron C McLaughlin Jr Errol Mills Bruce Palmer B Scott Ryder Patrick Taylor Joey Winfree ONeal D Subject FW Phil Let me know if this is ok Let ONeal know if you will be in or out so that we can get some fillers PL Original Message From Winfree ONeal D Sent Friday January PM To Love Phillip M Subject Phil Let me know if this is ok Gentlemen What Lets play poker Where The land of Pears When Thursday January th between pm Directions No key map so here goes South please find from Downtown Exit McHardShadow Creek hint its the first exit after the Beltway Take a left onto McHard and proceed to the end of McHard There will be a Conoco at the first Stop sign the next stop sign will say Country Place Proceed to the third stop Sign and take a left to The Lakes of Country Place Go to the Gurards gate You will visit Starleaf Go thru the gate and Take a left on River Birch drive Starleaf will be the rd street on the right My house is the th house on the left in the cul de sac address Starleaf Pearland Tx phone cell O

FW Message from Jimmy Coligan College PoolPST Original Message From James Coligan mailto Sent Monday January PM To Taylor Joey Cc Subject Re Message from Jimmy Coligan College Pool Hey everybody I have a friend doing a NFL playoff pool Here is how it works Rank every playoff team from being the team you think is going to win the Super Bowl and being a team you think will lose its first game You get points based on the number of points you put on each team that wins a game For instance if you put points on the Steelers this year and they will do this by the way they win the Super Bowl they will give you points for the divisional round for Conference Championship and for the Super Bowl The cost of the pool is and you can send me your money and picks and Ill pass it on to Brian I will need your picks by Wednesday if possible Jimmy wrote Hey Everybody Message from Jimmy with regard to the College Pool Take heed some of you owe him dinero Original Message From James Coligan SMTP Sent Monday January AM To Gibson Patrick L Subject RE Hey can you do me a favor and send out an update to the guys in our College Pool I dont have their emails here Matt Olney Mohammed Rhonda Robert Coligan Joey Taylor and Scott Let them know Todd Murray won the pot with a score of Several people were in the s including Joey Rhonda Matt Tracy and myself Also I still need cash from Rhonda Joey Mohammed Robert Scott My address is Boxelder Houston TX Thanks Jimmy Do You Yahoo Send FREE video emails in Yahoo Mail videomail
